rComments: His lectures are awful. He wears slippers everyday, sits down on a chair, and starts talking but no one has any idea what he is saying. Learned course material by myself. 100%. Quizzes and Assignment were easy. Final was brutal.

Boris is a very funny guy. I think he said his own lectures will be useless in his first class. Second lecture, he starts reading Wikipedia pages during lectures. Quizzes were very easy. Then things got even better as I find myself in company of 4 other students in a lecture with enrollment of 150 students. Exam was brutal. CR/NCR saved me.
